<p>Where a Health Plan has information about a memberâ€™s allergies the  <a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/us/core/StructureDefinition-us-core-allergyintolerance.html">US Core AllergyIntolerance profile</a>  <strong>SHALL</strong> be used to record them.</p>

<p>The essential fields to be provided in the US Core AllergyIntolerance resource are:</p>

